headline: Komatsu: The Cheaper Japanese Rival To Caterpillar At 9.6x TTM P/E
summary: Komatsu (KMTUY) offers a solid 4.38% dividend and has begun share repurchases, enhancing shareholder value. See why I think the stock is a buy.
